column2: Issue an  order in the  nature of writ of Mandamus compelling the  1St,  2nd  and 3rd  Respondents
to  hold an inquiry to  decide as  to whose name should be inserted according to law;
Issue an order in the nature of writ of Mandamus to thereafter insert the Petitioner's name as

the  owner  of  the  Agricultural  Land 
in 
the  Register  of  Permit/Grants  under 
the  Land
